description:
Application to vary conditions 1(Approved Plans), 7(Unit layouts), 24(Car Parking), 25(Basement levels) and 26(Disabled Parking) and to remove condition 5 (Residential entrance to Mitre Public House) of planning permission ref: P2018/2466/ S73 (and as previously amended and described by refs: P2013/2681/S73 and P2017/2866/S73, and ref: P090774) and to consolidate the following approved consents and details: 
- (P2014/2278/AOD) Approval of details pursuant to Condition 9 (Block C East Elevation Residential Entrance); 
- (P2014/2512/AOD) Approval of details pursuant to Condition 30 (Waste Management); 
- (P2018/2104/NMA) Non-Material amendment for a mezzanine floor to create additional office floorspace; 
- (P2018/2093/FUL) Permission for alterations and extensions to the former Mitre Public House; 
- (P2017/2866/S73) Amalgamation of layouts over 4 no. various sized residential units within Block C across sixth and seventh floors resulting in loss of 2 no. units (Total reduction 78 to 76 units) together with various minor elevational alterations principally relating to rerouting of smoke extract ducting;
- (P2018/1587/FUL) Permission for the amalgamation of retail units G16 and G22 to create a flexible A1/D1 use; 
- (P2019/1019/FUL) Permission for ground floor level alterations to provide a terrace for unit G22;
- (P2018/2466/S73) Variation of condition 44 to allow extended hours of use of approved Class D2 Use (Gym); 
- (P2019/1267/AOD) Partial Approval of details pursuant to condition 36 b, c, d, e, f, (Boundary treatments and pavement/footway treatments). 
The proposals include the following amendments to the layouts on the approved drawings: 
-       Minor plant and core layout alterations in the basement; 
-       Minor change to the layout of the bikes stores; 
